text: came here for breakfast. Old school taste. Tao Suan with you tiao not bad
Very nice You Tiao!! It's hot and not oily at all. Uncle is very friendly too.

The Perfect Crispy Delight

You Tiao a.k.a Chinese Cruller or Fried Dough Stick.
A cultural significance of the Chinese cuisine which symbolizes Prosperity & Togetherness.

I was delighted by the exquisite yet nostalgic flavour of the golden-brown You Tiao from this super friendly owners.

The satisfying crunch as you bite into its exterior with an enticing texture that gives way to a fluffy and airy middle with soft doughy center that practically melts in your mouth.

This is a must-try delicacy that promises to leave a lasting impression.

If you're a Youtiao lover, you MUST try Huan Le You Tiao. Even if you're not, after eating this you'll be a huge fan.

Rare JEM in the west! Very friendly owners too.
